source.name: Recycling Directory - Map View
source.description: A map view of all locations of businesses that take specific items for either recycling or disposal. Note: map shows only businesses that have a street address. A full list of establishments can be found at: https://data.edmonton.ca/Environmental-Services/Recycling-Directory/i2gf-u5vm
